From 5d6366ca1a8fab00718e24bf3e71faaf834bb842 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: DevMiner <devminer@devminer.xyz>
Date: Mon, 4 May 2026 21:40:36 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Add AHT family sensor support and increase neopixel
 BIT_MAX_TIME

Backport upstream Klipper AHT family support (AHT1X, AHT2X, AHT3X)
into Kalico while preserving danger_options and reconnect handler.

Increase neopixel BIT_MAX_TIME from 4us to 30us for BIGTREETECH MMS
LED communication compatibility.

Upstream-Status: Backport [https://github.com/Klipper3d/klipper/commit/1f43be0b8b55d90753578d06ac06356d1ab9a768]
---
 klippy/extras/aht10.py    | 148 +++++++++++++++++++++++---------------
 klippy/extras/neopixel.py |   2 +-
 2 files changed, 92 insertions(+), 58 deletions(-)

diff --git a/klippy/extras/aht10.py b/klippy/extras/aht10.py
index 3fcad83b..3e208178 100644
--- a/klippy/extras/aht10.py
+++ b/klippy/extras/aht10.py
